trans-unit.source: An XML element that configures the security for a service with endpoints that receive HTTP requests.
trans-unit.target: Elemento XML que configura la seguridad para un servicio con puntos de conexión que reciben solicitudes HTTP.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebHttpSecurityElement" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebHttpSecurityElement" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets an XML element that specifies the security mode for a basic HTTP service.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un elemento XML que especifica el modo de seguridad para un servicio HTTP básico.

trans-unit.source: A value of <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode" /> that indicates whether transport-level security or no security is used by an endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Valor de <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode" /> que indica si un extremo utiliza la seguridad del nivel de transporte o no usa seguridad.

trans-unit.source: This property determines whether the settings from the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurity.Transport%2A> property becomes effective.
trans-unit.target: Esta propiedad determina si los valores de la propiedad <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurity.Transport%2A> se vuelven efectivos.

trans-unit.source: The value is not a valid <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor no es un <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode" /> válido.

trans-unit.source: Gets an XML element that indicates the transport-level security settings for a service endpoint configured to receive HTTP requests.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un elemento XML que indica los valores de seguridad de nivel de transporte para un punto de conexión de servicio configurado para recibir las solicitudes HTTP.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebHttpSecurityElement" /> that specifies the transport-level security settings.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebHttpSecurityElement" /> que especifica la configuración de seguridad para el nivel de transporte.

trans-unit.source: The default values set are a <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity.ClientCredentialType" /> of <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.HttpClientCredentialType.None" />, a <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity.ProxyCredentialType" /> of <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.HttpProxyCredentialType.None" />, and <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity.Realm" /> = "".
trans-unit.target: El conjunto de valores predeterminados es <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity.ClientCredentialType" /> de <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.HttpClientCredentialType.None" />, <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity.ProxyCredentialType" /> de <see cref="F:System.ServiceModel.HttpProxyCredentialType.None" />, y <see cref="P:System.ServiceModel.HttpTransportSecurity.Realm" /> = "".

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebHttpSecurityElement> object returned by this property to set the transport security parameters.
trans-unit.target: Utilice el objeto <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebHttpSecurityElement> que devuelve esta propiedad para establecer los parámetros de seguridad de transporte.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode> must be set to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode.Transport> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode.TransportCredentialOnly> value for the settings provided by the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurity.Transport%2A> property to become effective for the service endpoint.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode> debe estar establecido en el valor <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode.Transport> o <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode.TransportCredentialOnly> para la configuración que proporciona la propiedad <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurity.Transport%2A> con el fin de hacerse efectivo en el extremo del servicio.

trans-unit.source: This value can be set in configuration or in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding.%23ctor%28System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode%29> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Este valor se puede establecer en la configuración o en el constructor <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding.%23ctor%28System.ServiceModel.WebHttpSecurityMode%29>.
